                        			<h1 itemprop="headline" id="headline" class="headline">What It Was Like Onstage During the Oscars 2017 Best Picture Mistake</h1>
	                                                <div id="story-meta-footer" class="story-meta-footer">
                                                                                                    

<p class="byline-dateline"><span class="byline" itemprop="author creator" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person"  itemid="https://www.nytimes.com/by/brooks-barnes">By <a href="https://www.nytimes.com/by/brooks-barnes" title="More Articles by BROOKS BARNES"><span class="byline-author" data-byline-name="BROOKS BARNES" itemprop="name" data-twitter-handle="brooksbarnesNYT">BROOKS BARNES</span></a> and </span><span class="byline" itemprop="author creator" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person"  itemid="https://www.nytimes.com/by/cara-buckley"><a href="https://www.nytimes.com/by/cara-buckley" title="More Articles by CARA BUCKLEY"><span class="byline-author" data-byline-name="CARA BUCKLEY" itemprop="name" data-twitter-handle="caraNYT">CARA BUCKLEY</span></a></span><time class="dateline" datetime="2017-02-28T07:31:47-05:00" itemprop="dateModified" content="2017-02-28T07:31:47-05:00">FEB. 27, 2017</time>
</p>

